overview.en: IXBTC is an off-chain operation network with a coherent technical and economic structure. Through this network, shared office studios and public welfare undertakings can be realized, and Internet-level scalability can be brought to the blockchain. The main application scenarios: public welfare payment + international patent products Docking and cooperation with companies in the health industry, plus shared office business as the main business.
overview.zh: IXBTC是具有连贯技术和经济架构的脱链运营网络，通过该网络可以实现共享办公工作室和公益事业，可将互联网级可扩展性带入区块链，主要应用场景：公益支付+国际专利产品与大健康产业等企业的对接与合作，加共享办公事业为主营业务。
